							<p>Foreign and domestic.  Oil prices are going up.  Gas prices are going up.  While we continue to drill for oil around the world, we’re not making more oil.  In fact, many scientists agree that we have already passed “peak oil”.  Peak oil is the point where 50% of the world’s oil is already consumed.  By carpooling you are contributing to a national effort that helps reduce our dependence on oil.  Together, we will make a massive change and lower our consumption.  Join us!</p> 
